    "rate_limits": "Rate limits vary by tier. Tier 1: 50 requests/min, 40K tokens/min. Higher tiers available",
    "context_windows": "Context windows range from 200K tokens (Claude 3 Opus/Sonnet/Haiku) to 100K (Claude 2)",
